PrecisRegulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1152 - FLUSILAZOLE) by setting a maximum limit (MRL) on residues of the pesticide flusilazole resulting from its use on apples, bananas, grapes and raisins, or that may remain in meat and meat by-products, and in milk.
